bio: Hello! I'm Aiswarya Dosibhatla, an experienced Data Analyst with 3+ years of experience in data analysis, ETL development, and business intelligence.
I'm proficient in Python, SQL, Power BI, Snowflake, and cloud platforms including Azure and AWS. I've delivered actionable insights, improving reporting accuracy by 25%.

My expertise includes designing dashboards, automating workflows, and optimizing data pipelines to enhance operational efficiency. I have a strong capability to translate business requirements into data-driven solutions for strategic initiatives.
